data.description: Enjoy country living near Imlay City on 10 acres, with this custom-built 3-bed, 3-bath ranch with large bedrooms. A full finished walkout basement features a third full bath.  Also has an attached garage.  Embrace serene pond views from the front and back, including a stocked pond with an island. Revel in a kitchen with charming hickory cabinets and a cozy breakfast nook. The Great Room boasts cathedral ceilings and a stone ledge fireplace. A 56 x 42 pole barn awaits with ample space for workshops and vehicle storage, currently set up for horses. Hunters will appreciate the abundant deer and turkey. Complete with a whole house Generac generator for added convenience, this property is perfect for relaxation or entertaining. BTAVAI
